members.comment: Constructs an UnsupportedAudioFileException that has null as its error detail message.
Constructs an UnsupportedAudioFileException that has the specified detail message.

param: message - a string containing the error detail message

name: javax.sound.sampled.UnsupportedAudioFileException
comment: An UnsupportedAudioFileException is an exception indicating that an operation failed because a file did not contain valid data of a recognized file type and format.
